UID:k5mVhq_V4CmUhjZcBo7on
SUMMARY:Open Coworking Day at Birch Road
DTSTAMP:20260307T230153Z
DTSTART:20260313T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:We're not your typical co-working space and our members wouldn'
	t have it any other way. ​\n\nIf you’re looking for a change of pace\, a b
	it of peace and quiet\, and a spot to call your own without being alone\, 
	you’ve found it. Experience the perfect blend of productivity and communit
