	eatures The Best Drink Specials and The Best Bars in Town.\n\nThis is a TW
	O DAY EVENT!\n\n🍀 Saturday\, March 14th: 2PM-2AM (Registration at SPIN: 2P
	M-8PM)\n\n🍀 Tuesday\, March 17th: 6PM-2AM (Registration at Villa Escondida
	: 6PM-11PM)\n\nPARTICIPATING BARS:\n\nSPIN (REGISTRATION - SAT\, 3/14) VIL
	LA ESCONDIDA (REGISTRATION - TUE 3/17) BLARNEY STONE IMPERIAL KITCHEN & BA
	R KELLS IRISH BAR JUPITER BAR PIKE PLACE BAR & GRILL SHAWN O'DONNELL'S\n\n
	Here is how it works:\n\n1) Pre-Purchase Your Bar Crawl Wristband.\n\n2) C
	heck in at SPIN (1511 6th Ave) on Saturday\, 3/14 & at VILLA ESCONDIDA (22
	03 1st Ave) on Tuesday\, 3/14 to get your wristband and map with participa
	ting bars\, their location\, and their drink specials. (Registration on Sa
	turday\, 3/14 from 2PM-8PM & Tuesday\, 3/17 from 6PM-11PM) \\***WRISTBAND 
	MUST BE PICKED UP DURING THESE TIMES**\\*\n\n3) Your wristband gets you in
	to any of the participating bars with no cover\, plus gets you drink speci
	als all night. \\***(Unless otherwise indicated by the maps)**\\*\n\n4) Ha
	ve Fun!\n\nFor questions\, email info@barcrawlerz.com or call (310) 273-87
